  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To identify the causative mutations in previously untreated patients with hemophilia A
      enrolled in the ReFacto® clinical safety and efficacy study CTN 93-R833-0XX/C9741-28, using
      two established hemophilia mutation testing laboratories (one in Europe and one in North
      America).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
